Why we moved away from it

The Excel file served us well, but over time it became difficult to maintain data quality. Duplicate entries, inconsistent naming, missing fields, and version conflicts when multiple people edited at the same time were common issues. There was no validation, no audit trail, and no way to track who changed what.

